Description: GMRS/HAM repeater controller daemon with DSP and web dashboard
 kerchunkd is a lightweight C11 repeater controller for GMRS radios using
 USB HID interfaces (CM108/CM119/RIM-Lite). It provides real-time CTCSS/DCS/DTMF
 decoding via libplcode, a priority audio queue with automatic PTT management,
 and a modular event-driven architecture with 24 dynamically loaded modules.
 .
 Features include CW ID (FCC 95.1751 compliant), weather announcements,
 NWS alert monitoring, text-to-speech via ElevenLabs, voicemail, call detail
 records, transmission recording, voice scrambler, SDR channel monitoring,
 FreeSWITCH autopatch, OTP authentication, and an embedded HTTPS web dashboard
 with real-time audio streaming via WebSocket.
 .
 This package provides the kerchunkd daemon, the kerchunk CLI, all modules,
 sound files, web dashboard, and systemd service.
